description: Ty Tucker is back with a vengeance. After losing to Dustin Michael, this badass requested another big guy. Spencer Reed is up for the challenge and does not mind adding another victory to his belt. Spencer had this wicked smile while he pound and ground his opponent. Ty can take a lot as he responds with some hard ass slapping of his own. Both studs fight to exhaustion to dominate in the final sex round.
title: Spencer Reed vs Ty Tucker
